                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7484" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0290</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2406 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">正合环保集团：破解流程瓶颈，持续运营改进</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Zhenghe Environmental Protection Group: Breaking Through Process Bottlenecks for Continuous Operational Improvement</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贾晓菁，谢炜铮，马沛瑶，刘梦瑶</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中央财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贾晓菁，谢炜铮，马沛瑶</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">正合环保集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农业环保企业；约束理论；瓶颈；流程改进；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Agricultural Environmental Protection Enterprise; Theory of Constraints; Bottleneck; Process Improvement</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了正合环保集团的业务流程设计和改进过程。公司创立之初，建立“三权分置”业务流程，探索出N2N区域生态循环农业新模式。之后，通过调整流程分工和定位，设立原料预处理环节，提升原料质量，再拓宽原料来源，成立农废中心，逐步搭建起一个以智慧农业为基础，囊括种植、养殖、加工等方面的综合服务平台，并进一步通过技术创新提高产品研发能力，不断开发新产品，延伸整个生产流程。通过阐述正合环保集团在企业发展过程中识别瓶颈并不断打破瓶颈的历程，引导学生理解流程改进的原理和方法，掌握约束理论及其在企业流程改进中的应用，并且正确理解流程瓶颈的概念，能够识别流程中不同类型的瓶颈，并懂得通过提升瓶颈的产出而改善流程绩效，进而实现可持续运营。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the design and improvement process of Zhenghe Environmental Protection Group&#39;s business operations. At the outset, the company established a business process called &#39;Separation of Three Rights&#39; and explored a novel model of regional ecological cycle agriculture known as the N2N mode. Subsequently, by adjusting workflow roles and positioning, implementing a raw material pretreatment step, enhancing the quality of raw materials, diversifying the source of raw materials, and creating an agricultural waste center, the company gradually constructed a comprehensive service platform based on smart agriculture. This platform, encompassing planting, breeding, processing, and more, further augmented product development capabilities through technological innovation, continuously cultivated new products, and extended the entire production process. By elucidating the progression of Zhenghe Environmental Protection Group identifying and continually overcoming bottlenecks during its growth, the case guides students to understand the principles and methods of process improvement, master the Theory of Constraints and its application in business process improvement. Furthermore, it aids students in comprehending the concept of process bottlenecks accurately, equipping them with the ability to identify different types of bottlenecks in the process, and understand how to enhance process performance by elevating the output of the bottleneck, thereby facilitating sustainable operations.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《运营管理》、《管理理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">约束理论；流程改进</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
